headline: Is The Trade Desk (TTD) One of the Best Fundamental Stocks to Buy According to Analysts?
summary: The Trade Desk, Inc. (NASDAQ:TTD) is one of the Best Fundamental Stocks to Buy According to Analysts. On January 12, Wells Fargo reduced the firm’s price objective on the company’s stock to $42 from $47, while keeping an “Equal Weight” rating, as reported by The Fly. The firm expects an in-line EPS.
